
<p>It&#8217;s finally the 2020s. After 20 years of not being able to refer to the decade we&#8217;re in, we&#8217;re all finally free—in the clear for the next 80 years until 2100, at which point I assume <a href="https://waitbutwhy.com/2015/01/artificial-intelligence-revolution-1.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AGI</a> will have figured out what to call the two decades between 2100 and 2120. </p>
<p>We now live in the 20s! It&#8217;s exciting. &#8220;The twenties&#8221; is super legit-sounding, and it&#8217;s so old school. The 40s are old. The 30s even more so. But nothing is older school than the Roaring 20s.</p>
<p>We&#8217;re now in charge of making this a cool decade so when people 100 years from now are thinking about how incredibly old-timey the 2020s were, it&#8217;s old-timey in a cool appealing way and not a boring shitty way.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s also weird that to us, the 2020s sounds like such a rad futuristic decade—and that&#8217;s how the 1920s seemed to people 100 years ago today. They were all used to the 19-teens, and suddenly they were like, &#8220;whoa cool we&#8217;re in the <em>twenties!&#8221; </em>Then they got upset thinking about how much farther along in life their 1910 self thought they&#8217;d be by 1920.</p>
<p>In any case, it&#8217;s a perfect time for one of those &#8220;shit we&#8217;re old&#8221; posts.</p>
<p>So here are some New Years 2020 time facts:</p>
<p>When World War 2 started, the Civil War felt as far away to Americans as WW2 feels to us now.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8735" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1.png" alt="" width="1178" height="175" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1.png 1178w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1-600x89.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1-768x114.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1-750x111.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 1178px) 100vw, 1178px" /></a></p>
<p>Speaking of World War 2, the world wars were pretty close together. If World War 2 were starting today, World War 1 would feel about as far back to us as 9/11.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/7.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-8733 aligncenter" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/7.png" alt="" width="520" height="267" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/7.png 649w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/7-600x308.png 600w " sizes="(max-width: 520px) 100vw, 520px" /></a></p>
<p>The Soviet Union break up is now as distant a memory as JFK&#8217;s assassination was when the Soviet Union broke up.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-1.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8742" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-1.png" alt="" width="1204" height="214" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-1.png 1204w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-1-600x107.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-1-768x137.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-1-750x133.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 1204px) 100vw, 1204px" /></a></p>
<p>Moving on to more inane topics, there have been more Super Bowls since the 1993 Cowboys–Bills SB than before it.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8728" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2.png" alt="" width="1249" height="246" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2.png 1249w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2-600x118.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2-768x151.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2-750x148.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 1249px) 100vw, 1249px" /></a></p>
<p>And West Germany&#8217;s 1974 World Cup victory happened closer to the first World Cup in 1930 than to today.</p>
<p><em>The Wonder Years </em>aired from 1988 and 1993 and depicted the years between 1968 and 1973. When I watched the show, it felt like it was set in a time long ago. If a new Wonder Years premiered today, it would cover the years between 2000 and 2005.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6-1.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-8736 aligncenter" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6-1.png" alt="" width="553" height="323" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6-1.png 701w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/6-1-600x351.png 600w " sizes="(max-width: 553px) 100vw, 553px" /></a></p>
<p>Also, remember when <em>Jurassic Park</em>, <em>The Lion King</em>, and <em>Forrest Gump </em>came out in theaters? Closer to the moon landing than today.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/8.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8734" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/8.png" alt="" width="1146" height="229" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/8.png 1146w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/8-600x120.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/8-768x153.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/8-750x150.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 1146px) 100vw, 1146px" /></a></p>
<p>Y2K? Closer to the 70s than today.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/9-1.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8745" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/9-1.png" alt="" width="1060" height="174" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/9-1.png 1060w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/9-1-600x98.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/9-1-768x126.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/9-1-750x123.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 1060px) 100vw, 1060px" /></a></p>
<p>Meanwhile, the O.J. Simpson trial is now half way between the 1960s and today. And closer to the Charles Manson trial.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/10-2.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8747" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/10-2.png" alt="" width="953" height="197" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/10-2.png 953w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/10-2-600x124.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/10-2-768x159.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/10-2-750x155.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 953px) 100vw, 953px" /></a></p>
<p>As for you, if you&#8217;re 60 or older, you were born closer to the 1800s than today.</p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4-1.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8750" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4-1.png" alt="" width="1199" height="179" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4-1.png 1199w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4-1-600x90.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4-1-768x115.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/4-1-750x112.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 1199px) 100vw, 1199px" /></a></p>
<p>Today&#8217;s 35-year-olds were born closer to the 1940s than to today. </p>
<p><a href="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5-1.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-8751" src="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5-1.png" alt="" width="1202" height="186" srcset="https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5-1.png 1202w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5-1-600x93.png 600w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5-1-768x119.png 768w , https://149909199.v2.pressablecdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/5-1-750x116.png 750w " sizes="(max-width: 1202px) 100vw, 1202px" /></a></p>
<p>There are a lot of options for that kind of calculation, but those two seemed like the most depressing to me. Worth mentioning that my 94-year-old grandmother was born closer to the Andrew Jackson administration than to today.</p>
<p>If you were born in the 1980s like me, a kid today who&#8217;s the age you were in 1990 is a full 30-year generation younger than you. They&#8217;ll remember Obama&#8217;s presidency the way you remember Reagan&#8217;s. 9/11 to them is the moon landing for you. The 90s seem as ancient to them as the 60s seem to you. To you, the 70s are just a little before your time—that&#8217;s how they think of the 2000s. They see the 70s how you see the 40s. And the hippy 60s seems as old to them as the Great Depression seems to you. </p>
<p>But the weirdest thing about kids today: most of them will live to see the 2100s.</p>
<p>Sorry if this stressed you out. Happy New Year!</p>
